e%20take%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyearly-multigenerational-family-trip-is-one-of-my-cherished-memories-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esame%20trip%20every%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20get%20varying%20reactions.%20My%20friends%20have%20asked%20why%20we%20didn't%20spend%20that%20time%20going%20somewhere%20new.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20about%20Yosemite%3F%20Or%20the%20Grand%20Canyon%3F%26quot%3B%20I'd%20argue%20that%20people%20with%20summer%20houses%20and%20timeshares%20went%20to%20the%20same%20place%20year%20after%20year%3B%20why%20couldn't%20we%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20there%20are%20advantages%20to%20our%20trip.%20It%20saves%20time%20and%20money%20%E2%80%94%20not%20only%20is%20it%20close%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20waste%20money%20trying%20things%20out%20that%20we%20may%20not%20like.%20And%20it%20serves%20as%20a%20family%20tradition%20that%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20going%20to%20the%20same%20vacation%20spot%20can%20be%20soothing.%20For%20me%2C%20going%20to%20Lake%20Arrowhead%20every%20year%20is%20like%20re-watching%20a%20favorite%20TV%20show%3A%20it's%20fun%2C%20easy%2C%20and%20I%20know%20what%20to%20expect.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcivicscience.com%2Fas-vacation-season-heats-up-many-americans-are-feeling-stressed-over-travel-planning%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%202024%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2019%25%20of%20US%20adults%20say%20planning%20a%20trip%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20stressful.%26quot%3B%20That%20number%20bumps%20up%20to%2026%25%20for%20those%20traveling%20with%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20believe%20it.%20When%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20did%20take%20other%20trips%20throughout%20my%20childhood%2C%20like%20the%20winter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-trip-new-york-city-frequent-traveler-best-worst-parts-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewe%20went%20to%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20our%20vacation%20to%20Hawaii%2C%20she%20was%20stressed%20researching%20activities%20and%20restaurants%20in%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20preparation%20for%20our%20Lake%20Arrowhead%20weekends%2C%20she%20simply%20calls%20the%20hotel%20and%20books%20it.%20No%20additional%20work%2C%20and%20no%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20seeing%20new%20places%20is%20great%2C%20even%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20whenever%20I%20go%20to%20a%20new%20city%2C%20seeing%20new%20sights%20and%20eating%20new%20foods%2C%20I%20come%20back%20feeling%20like%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspending-alone-time-when-traveling-with-friends-and-family-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eneed%20a%20vacation%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20my%20vacation.%20But%20when%20I%20come%20back%20from%20my%20annual%20Lake%20Arrowhead%20trip%2C%20I%20feel%20relaxed%2C%20refreshed%2C%20and%20ready%20to%20get%20back%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20mom%20on%20a%20boat%20at%20Lake%20Arrowhead.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887d09085e81483682eccd9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20enjoy%20activities%20like%20making%20s'mores%2C%20visiting%20the%20lakeside%20village%2C%20and%20waterskiing.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jillian%20Pretzel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b842cc9-a01d-4639-a399-1c3ca8fdba5d%5C%22%3EIt's%20budget-friendly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20summer%2C%20when%20I%20checked%20into%20the%20hotel%20for%20our%20annual%20trip%2C%20the%20woman%20at%20the%20front%20desk%20asked%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20buy%20a%20%2430%20s'mores%20kit%2C%20and%20I%2C%20of%20course%2C%20politely%20declined.%20We%20always%20stop%20in%20at%20the%20same%20local%20grocery%20store%20when%20we%20drive%20in%20and%20pick%20up%20the%20same%20s'mores%20fixings%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20drinks.%20I'v