ounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20also%20consider%20valuation%20advisory%20teams%20or%20businesses.%20Some%20banks%2C%20for%20example%2C%20have%20valuation%20advisory%20practices%20that%20are%20separate%20from%20their%20investment%20bank%20but%20that%20work%20with%20the%20investment%20banking%20coverage%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f2b376cb-0955-4578-a431-02e63c387669%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsider%20a%20master's%20degree%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20also%20buy%20yourself%20another%20year%20of%20recruiting%20by%20enrolling%20in%20a%20master's%20finance%20program%20(different%20from%20an%20MBA%2C%20which%20you%20could%20still%20do%20later).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20way%20to%20extend%20the%20runway%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sibley%2C%20who%20is%20associate%20chair%20of%20IU's%20master%20of%20science%20in%20finance%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20has%20had%20students%20go%20this%20route%20at%20IU%20and%20land%20a%20job%20before.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20one-year%20specialized%20programs%20at%20various%20universities%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20to%20a%20different%20school%20than%20where%20you%20did%20undergrad%20is%20probably%20better%2C%20he%20said%2C%20so%20you%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20a%20second%20alumni%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20easier%20to%20find%20a%20job%20from%20school%20than%20from%20your%20parents'%20basement%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sibley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-internships-return-offers-advice-jobs-investment-banking-analysts-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754125201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688cfc8385e81483682f259b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-internships-return-offers-advice-jobs-investment-banking-analysts-2025-8%22%