0the%20second%20COVID-19%20wave%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20noticed%20an%20increasing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328846%2Fsibi-manivannan-runs-gramiya-cold-pressed-oils-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemand%20for%20cold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20insight%20led%20them%20to%20pivot%20their%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202022%2C%20the%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20team%20ventured%20into%20the%20cold-pressed%20oil%20market%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20Foreka%20in%20Rajasthan.%20This%20expansion%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20the%20support%20Satyam%20received%20in%20November%202020%2C%20when%20he%20was%20awarded%20a%20prestigious%20fellowship%20from%20The%20Buddha%20Institute%2C%20founded%20by%20Ved%20Arya%2C%20an%20alumnus%20of%20IIM%20Ahmedabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Buddha%20Institute%20provided%20us%20with%20a%20generous%20grant%20of%20Rs%2022%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20which%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20enabling%20the%20team%20to%20scale%20their%20operations.%20Their%20research%20into%20the%20region%20highlighted%20a%20high%20rate%20of%20outmigration%2C%20presenting%20an%20opportunity%20to%20create%20local%20employment.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20exceptional%20quality%20of%20mustard%20seeds%20in%20the%20area%20made%20it%20an%20ideal%20location%20for%20their%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20partnered%20with%20NGOs%20like%20SRIJAN%20to%20establish%20a%20value%20chain%20for%20farming%2C%20offering%20farmers%20better%20prices%20and%20resources%20to%20test%20seed%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20supporting%20farmers%20directly%2C%20we%20ensured%20fair%20prices%20and%20sustainable%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satyam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20breakthrough%20came%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20processing%20unit%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%2C%20Rajasthan.%20The%20setup%20includes%20cold-pressed%20machines%20owned%20by%20the%20farmers%2C%20while%20Foreka%20works%20on%20a%20co-profit%20model%2C%20sharing%2050%25%20of%20the%20profits%20after%20covering%20costs.%20Partnering%20with%20two%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisations%20(FPOs)%2C%20one%20near%20Jhansi%20and%20the%20other%20in%20the%20Chambal%20Valley%2C%20Foreka%20sources%20groundnuts%2C%20processes%20them%2C%20and%20sells%20groundnut%20oil.%20The%20model%20helps%20reduce%20outmigration%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311715%2Fbengaluru-social-impact-startup-mikro-grafeio-creates-employment-in-tier-ii-and-iii-indian-cities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20local%20employment%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Their%20breakthrough%20came%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20processing%20unit%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%2C%20Rajasthan.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-479455%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETheir%20breakthrough%20came%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20processing%20unit%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%2C%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20given%20me%20financial%20stability%2C%20pride%20in%20my%20work%2C%20and%20a%20brighter%20future%20for%20my%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramavtar%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20farmer.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20farmer%20with%20divided%20land%20and%20unpredictable%20income%2C%20life%20was%20tough.%20I%20struggled%20to%20provide%20for%20my%20family%20and%20lacked%20opportunities%20for%20my%20children.%20But%20joining%20Foreka%20changed%20everything.%20They%20offered%20fair%20prices%20for%20my%20mustard%20seeds%2C%20which%20boosted%20my%20income%2C%20and%20trained%20me%20to%20operate%20machines%2C%20giving%20me%20a%20steady%20job.%20Now%2C%20my%20children%20are%20receiving%20an%20education%2C%20and%20one%20is%20pursuing%20a%20degree%20in%20Veterinary%20Sciences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20are%20treated%20as%20partners%2C%20not%20just%20suppliers.%20They%20have%20a%20direct%20stake%20in%20the%20success%20of%20the%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satyam.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20model%20ensures%20that%20they%20are%20as%20invested%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20business%20as%20we%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20challenges%2C%20building%20a%20brand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20faced%20a%20series%20of%20significant%20challenges%20as%20they%20expanded%20their%20business.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20difficult%20to%20raise%20funds%20after%20becoming%20a%20private%20limited%20company.%20There%20are%20very%20few%20impact%20investors%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20entrepreneurship%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20challenge%20was%20their%20inexperience.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20driven%20by%20willpower%2C%20but%20we%20had%20little%20experience%20and%20lacked%20the%20necessary%20skills.%20We%20realised%20that%20skills%20are%20developed%20through%20experience.%20So%2C%20we%20took%20the%20time%20to%20seek%20mentoring%20in%20areas%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F298011%2Fgurugram-retired-woman-starts-ayurvedic-veena-jis-hair-oil-business-to-reduce-hair-fall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarketing%20and%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20major%20challenge%20came%20when%20the%20trio%20encountered%20their%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20fraud%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20taken%20a%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20loan%20to%20procure%20oil%20from%20farmers%2C%20and%20we%20received%20our%20first%20order%20in%20July%202022%2C%20a%20300-litre%20batch%20of%20cold-pressed%20oil.%20The%20order%20was%20valued%20around%20Rs%206-7%20lakh%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20send%20it%20to%20Noida%20in%20the%20NCR%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20worked%20all%20night%20packing%20and%20preparing%20the%20shipment%2C%20and%20I%20went%20to%20collect%20the%20payment.%20The%20vendor%20told%20me%20that%20his%20bank%20account%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20working%20and%20that%20he%20could%20only%20transfer%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20initially%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20was%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20their%20troubles.%20The%20vendor%20ended%20up%20not%20paying%20the%20remaining%20Rs%204%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20huge%20challenge.%20To%20repay%20the%20loan%2C%20we%20had%20to%20raise%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20from%20friends%20and%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%20difficulties%20but%20also%20being%20grateful%20for%20the%20support%20he%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%