.%20He%20is%20quick%20to%20credit%20the%20community%20for%20sparking%20and%20sustaining%20this%20change.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20community%20that%20first%20identified%20and%20alerted%20me%20about%20the%20problem.%20Now%2C%20they%20remain%20vigilant.%20They%20report%20to%20me%20directly%20if%20they%20see%20any%20trucks%20trying%20to%20dump%20waste%2C%20or%20when%20the%20gardener%20is%20on%20leave%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20most%20dedicated%20guardians%20is%20Antram.%20He%20took%20it%20upon%20himself%20to%20protect%20the%20site%20from%20further%20harm.%20He%20watches%20over%20the%20spot%2C%20ensuring%20no%20one%20contaminates%20it%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20come%20here%20to%20plant%20trees.%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20check%20that%20no%20cattle%20damage%20them.%20With%20the%20rain%2C%20the%20trees%20look%20lush%20and%20green.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20garbage%20to%20be%20seen%2C%20no%20unpleasant%20odour.%20It%E2%80%99s%20refreshing%20now.%20Customers%20can%20now%20sit%20at%20my%20stall%20without%20foul%20smells%20bothering%20them.%20My%20business%20is%20also%20doing%20well%20because%20people%20are%20more%20willing%20to%20visit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20journey%20was%20far%20from%20easy.%20Early%20funding%20rejections%20were%20disheartening%2C%20and%20convincing%20companies%20to%20invest%20in%20land%20restoration%20proved%20challenging.%20Many%20felt%20the%20work%20required%20too%20much%20effort%20with%20little%20visible%20outcome%20in%20the%20short%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Vikrant%E2%80%99s%20determination%20never%20faltered.%20He%20continued%20approaching%20corporate%20allies%20and%20individuals%2C%20explaining%20why%20this%20effort%20mattered.%20Eventually%2C%20with%20support%20through%20CSR%20funds%20and%20personal%20contributions%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20gather%20the%20resources%20needed.%20In%20total%2C%20transformi