E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Bakul%20Foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20volunteer-driven%20movement%20in%20Odisha%20enabling%20public%20initiatives%20like%20free%20libraries%20and%20art%20programmes.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESambad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20major%20Odia%20news%20outlet.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoonj%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20humanitarian%20organisation%20working%20on%20disaster%20relief%20and%20rural%20development.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESELCO%20Foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20develops%20decentralised%20renewable%20energy-based%20solutions.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20way%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20weather%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Socratus%20began%20looking%20for%20a%20place%20to%20test%20its%20ideas%2C%20Odisha%20felt%20like%20the%20obvious%20choice.%20The%20state%20lives%20under%20the%20constant%20threat%20of%20cyclones%20and%20floods.%20Its%20landscapes%20%E2%80%94%20from%20dense%20forests%20to%20fragile%20coastlines%20%E2%80%94%20are%20among%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdisha%20also%20had%20a%20strong%20base%20to%20build%20on.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20state%20to%20adopt%20a%20comprehensive%20climate%20action%20plan%2C%20with%20systems%20stretching%20from%20the%20grassroots%20to%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20important%20are%20the%20people.%20Nearly%2023%20percent%20of%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20population%20belongs%20to%2064%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20Twelve%20out%20of%20its%2030%20districts%20are%20tribal-dominated%2C%20home%20to%20communities%20living%20across%20forests%2C%20wetlands%2C%20farmlands%2C%20and%20coastal%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20its%20philosophy%20to%20life%2C%20Socratus%20teamed%20up%20with%20organisations%20like%20Sambad%20and%20Bakul%20Foundation%20and%20launched%20the%20Climate%20Panchayat%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-500x855.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20colourful%20maps%20of%20Odisha%20showing%20groundwater%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20extreme%20weather%20trends.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-500x855.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-175x300.jpg%20175w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-768x1314.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-898x1536.jpg%20898w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-150x257.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935.jpg%20988w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-478542%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20sessions%20bring%20together%20all%20the%20stakeholders%20of%20a%20locality%20%E2%80%94%20men%2C%20women%2C%20farmers%2C%20forest%20workers%2C%20youth%2C%20scientists%2C%20and%20even%20MLAs%20sometimes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Devjit.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20gets%20a%20chance%20to%20share%20grievances%2C%20ideas%2C%20and%20solutions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meetings%20are%20organised%20around%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20147%20legislative%20constituencies%20%E2%80%94%20a%20conscious%20choice%20to%20match%20political%20boundaries%20and%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20track%20progress.%20The%20larger%20vision%3F%20To%20turn%20Climate%20Panchayat%20into%20a%20governance%20tool%20that%20can%20work%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocratus%20also%20facilitates%20other%20gatherings%2C%20such%20as%20Gram%20Swabhiman%20(in%20collaboration%20with%20Goonj%20and%20Nature%E2%80%99s%20Club)%2C%20where%20only%20community%20members%20come%20together%20to%20rebuild%20confidence%20and%20ownership%20over%20their%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20launch%2C%20152%20Climate%20Panchayats%20and%2048%20Gram%20Swabhiman%20meetings%20have%20been%20held.%20Over%2010%2C000%20citizens%20have%20participated%20directly%2C%20while%20more%20than%20two%20lakh%20people%20have%20engaged%20through%20Sambad%E2%80%99s%20print%2C%20digital%2C%20and%20social%20media.%20The%20impact%20is%20visible%20%E2%80%94%20insights%20from%20these%20conversations%20have%20already%20reached%20the%20Odisha%20Assembly%2C%20with%2020%20MLAs%20raising%20climate%20issues%20based%20on%20what%20communities%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753884698.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Community%20meetings%20in%20Bhitarkanika%20give%20families%20a%20platform%20to%20plan%20solutions%20to%20local%20climate%20challenges.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753884698.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753884698-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753884698-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753884698-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753884698-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-478547%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECommunity%20meetings%20in%20Bhitarkanika%20give%20families%20a%20platform%20to%20plan%20solutions%20to%20local%20climate%20challenges.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20striking%20outcome%20of%20these%20efforts%20is%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Climate%20Atlas%20%E2%80%94%20a%20set%20of%20visual%20maps%20and%20datasets%20tracking%20groundwater%20levels%2C%20rainfall%20changes%2C%20and%20extreme%20weather%20events.%20Built%20using%20community%20surveys%20and%20satellite%20data%2C%20the%20atlas%20helps%20policymakers%20design%20responses%20rooted%20in%20ground%20realities%2C%20not%20assumptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMeetings%20that%20bring%20back%20forests%20and%20fields%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bhitarkanika%2C%20conversations%20at%20these%20meetings%20often%20circle%20back%20to%20the%20same%20struggles%3A%20shrinking%20livelihoods%2C%20saltwater%20creeping%20into%20farmlands%2C%20and%20wildlife%20attacks%20that%20are%20becoming%20more%20frequent.%20Erratic%20rainfall%20has%20pushed%20families%20to%20abandon%20paddy%20cultivation%20and%20fishing%2C%20turning%20instead%20to%20prawn%20farming%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20it%E2%80%99s%20illegal.%20But%20that%2C%20too%2C%20brings%20heartbreak%2C%20as%20prawn%20mortality%20wipes%20out%20their%20investment%20and%20leaves%20them%20in%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForest%20access%20has%20tightened%20under%20conservation%20laws%2C%20cutting%20people%20off%20from%20essentials%20like%20honey%2C%20crabs%2C%20and%20nalia%20grass%20used%20for%20weaving%20baskets.%20For%20many%2C%20the%20choice%20has%20been%20stark%20%E2%80%94%20break%20the%20law%20or%20leave%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20where%20these%20gatherings%20have%20begun%20to%20make%20a%20difference.%20They%20are%20not%20just%20spaces%20for%20talk%3B%20they%20are%20where%20local%20voices%20are%20shaping%20local%20action.%20In%20Kendrapara%20district%2C%20insights%20from%20Climate%20Panchayats%20and%20Gram%20Swabhiman%20sessions%20have%20sparked%20large-scale%20community%20plantations%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20along%20riverbanks%2C%20but%20across%20schoolyards%2C%20village%20commons%2C%20and%20temple%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753882641.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Climate%20Panchayats%20unite%20villagers%2C%20experts%2C%20and%20officials%20to%20co-create%20solutions%20for%20climate%20resilience.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753882641.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753882641-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753882641-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753882641-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753882641-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-478520%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EClimate%20Panchayats%20unite%20villagers%2C%20experts%2C%20and%20officials%20to%20co-create%20solutions%20for%20climate%20resilience.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20are%20also%20bringing%20back%20traditional%20varieties%20of%20aromatic%20rice%20%E2%80%94%20Leelavati%2C%20Basuabhoga%2C%20and%20Haladigundi.%20These%20grains%20are%20more%20than%20food%3B%20they%20are%20organic%2C%20resilient%2C%20and%20rooted%20in%20local%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20ideas%20don%E2%80%99t%20stop%20at%20the%20fields.%20From%20these%20conversations%20have%20come%20plans%20for%20the%20future.%20Socratus%2C%20along%20with%20SELCO%20and%20Nature%E2%80%99s%20Club%2C%20is%20working%20to%20install%20solar-powered%20food%20processors%20and%20set%20up%20new%20livelihood%20options%20like%20puffed%20rice%20units%2C%20mushroom%20cultivation%20centres%2C%20and%20agarbatti-making%20setups.%20A%20prototype%20is%20even%20in%20the%20works%20to%20replace%20diesel%20and%20petrol%20boats%20in%20Bhitarkanika%20National%20Park%20with%20solar-powered%20ones.%20All%20of%20this%20began%20with%20people%20sitting%20together%20and%20sharing%20their%20needs%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reminder%20that%20when%20communities%20lead%2C%20solutions%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20want%20to%20help%20others%20turn%20their%20lives%20around%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20driving%20this%20change%20are%20120%20local%20women%20trained%20by%20Nature%E2%80%99s%20Club%20as%20Climate%20Champions%20under%20the%20Odisha%20government%E2%80%99s%20ECRICC%20(Enhancing%20Climate%20Resilience%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Coastal%20Communities)%20project.%20They%20spread%20awareness%2C%20share%20practical%20knowledge%2C%20and%20have%20become%20trusted%20voices%20in%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%20is%20Sabita%20Behera%2C%20whose%20life%20reflects%20both%20the%20struggles%20and%20strength%20of%20Bhitarkanika.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESabita%20was%20just%2012%20when%20she%20lost%20her%20mother.%20With%20an%20ailing%20father%20and%20a%20younger%20brother%20to%20care%20for%2C%20she%20often%20had%20to%20beg%20for%20money%20to%20cover%20hospital%20bills%20in%20Cuttack.%20She%20married%20young%20and%2C%20like%20many%20from%20Odisha%2C%20migrated%20with%20her%20husband%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20work%20